title: #92Noon Vox In The Box! Boudreau/McGuire/Carter/Modano/Ramsey
description: The undefeated Vox In The Box is back! Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau joins the show at the start, NBC Sports Network's Pierre McGuire talks NHL Hockey, Former Wild and White Bear Lake Bear Ryan Carter brings his perspective about the Wild to the box, Wild Executive Advisor Mike Modano stops by and Rachel Ramsey sits in for the Distraction Factor!
